						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1214, Nandana (= A.D. 1292-93), Phālguṇa,</hi> in the reign of the Yādava king <hi rend="bold">Vīra-Rāmachandrarāya.</hi> It records that the <hi rend="italic">Manneyagoḍiti</hi> <hi rend="bold">Chaṭṭarasa</hi> fought at the command of <hi rend="bold">Kandharadēva,</hi> and died after beheading a number of enemies.</p>						

